The code for this project makes use of the WiringPi library, a PIN based GPIO access library for the BCM2835, BCM2836 and BCM2837 SoC devices used in all Raspberry Pi computers.

The WiringPi library is licensed under the GNU LGPL, version 3.

More information on WiringPi can be found at http://wiringpi.com/

